### ============================================================
###  VOICE Backend — Full Test Suite v2
###  כולל: Flask | Auth | Users | Analysis | System Flows
###
###  סדר הרצה:
###    1. הפעל Flask: python ml/app.py  (פורט 5001)
###    2. הפעל Spring Boot              (פורט 8080)
###    3. הרץ Section 0 (health checks)
###    4. הרץ Section 1 (login) → העתק tokens
###    5. הרץ את שאר הבדיקות לפי סדר
### ============================================================

@backendUrl  = http://localhost:8080
@flaskUrl    = http://localhost:5001

@adminToken  = PASTE_ADMIN_TOKEN_HERE
@userToken   = PASTE_USER_TOKEN_HERE
@refreshToken = PASTE_REFRESH_TOKEN_HERE
@createdUserId = PASTE_CREATED_USER_ID_HERE
@analysisId    = PASTE_ANALYSIS_ID_HERE
@testWav       = PASTE_FULL_PATH_TO_WAV_HERE


###
### ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
###  SECTION 0 │ FLASK SERVICE
### ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### 0.1  Flask health ✅ (צפוי: 200 + ready: true)
GET {{flaskUrl}}/health

###

### 0.2  ניתוח ישיר ל-Flask ✅ (ללא Java — בודק את ה-ML בלבד)
POST {{flaskUrl}}/analyze
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "file_path": "{{testWav}}"
}

###

### 0.3  Flask — קובץ לא קיים ❌ (צפוי: 404)
POST {{flaskUrl}}/analyze
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "file_path": "C:/does/not/exist/fake.wav"
}

###

### 0.4  Flask — גוף ריק ❌ (צפוי: 400)
POST {{flaskUrl}}/analyze
Content-Type: application/json

{}


###
### ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
###  SECTION 1 │ AUTHENTICATION
### ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### 1.1  Login Admin ✅
POST {{backendUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "admin123"
}

###

### 1.2  Login User ✅
POST {{backendUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "user",
  "password": "user123"
}

###

### 1.3  Login — סיסמה שגויה ❌ (צפוי: 401)
POST {{backendUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "wrongpassword"
}

###

### 1.4  Login — משתמש לא קיים ❌ (צפוי: 401)
POST {{backendUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "ghost_user",
  "password": "doesntmatter"
}

###

### 1.5  Login — שדות ריקים ❌ (צפוי: 400)
POST {{backendUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "",
  "password": ""
}

###

### 1.6  Refresh Token תקין ✅ (צפוי: 200 + tokens חדשים)
POST {{backendUrl}}/api/auth/refresh-token
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "refreshToken": "{{refreshToken}}"
}

###

### 1.7  Refresh Token מזויף ❌ (צפוי: 401)
POST {{backendUrl}}/api/auth/refresh-token
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "refreshToken": "this.is.a.fake.token"
}

###

### 1.8  Refresh Token ריק ❌ (צפוי: 400)
POST {{backendUrl}}/api/auth/refresh-token
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "refreshToken": ""
}

###

### 1.9  Logout ✅ (צפוי: 204)
POST {{backendUrl}}/api/auth/logout
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

###

### 1.10  שימוש בtoken אחרי Logout ❌ (צפוי: 401)
GET {{backendUrl}}/api/users
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}


###
### ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
###  SECTION 2 │ USER MANAGEMENT
### ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### 2.1  GET כל המשתמשים — Admin ✅
GET {{backendUrl}}/api/users
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### 2.2  GET כל המשתמשים — User ✅ (USER מורשה ל-GET)
GET {{backendUrl}}/api/users
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

###

### 2.3  GET משתמש ID=1 ✅
GET {{backendUrl}}/api/users/1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### 2.4  GET משתמש לא קיים ❌ (צפוי: 404)
GET {{backendUrl}}/api/users/9999
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### 2.5  GET ללא token ❌ (צפוי: 401)
GET {{backendUrl}}/api/users

###

### 2.6  GET עם token מזויף ❌ (צפוי: 401)
GET {{backendUrl}}/api/users
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9.fake.signature

###

### 2.7  POST יצירת משתמש — Admin ✅ (שמור ID → @createdUserId)
POST {{backendUrl}}/api/users
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "testuser_new",
  "email":    "testuser@voice.ai",
  "roles":    []
}

###

### 2.8  POST יצירת משתמש — User ❌ (צפוי: 403)
POST {{backendUrl}}/api/users
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "should_fail",
  "email":    "fail@voice.ai",
  "roles":    []
}

###

### 2.9  POST email לא תקין ❌ (צפוי: 400)
POST {{backendUrl}}/api/users
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "validname",
  "email":    "not-an-email",
  "roles":    []
}

###

### 2.10  PUT עדכון — Admin ✅
PUT {{backendUrl}}/api/users/{{createdUserId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "testuser_updated",
  "email":    "updated@voice.ai",
  "roles":    []
}

###

### 2.11  PUT עדכון — User ❌ (צפוי: 403)
PUT {{backendUrl}}/api/users/{{createdUserId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "hack_attempt",
  "email":    "hack@voice.ai",
  "roles":    []
}

###

### 2.12  DELETE — Admin ✅ (צפוי: 204)
DELETE {{backendUrl}}/api/users/{{createdUserId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### 2.13  DELETE שוב — אותו ID ❌ (צפוי: 404)
DELETE {{backendUrl}}/api/users/{{createdUserId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### 2.14  DELETE — User ❌ (צפוי: 403)
DELETE {{backendUrl}}/api/users/1
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}


###
### ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
###  SECTION 3 │ ANALYSIS — HAPPY PATH (Java → Flask → DB)
### ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### 3.1  Upload WAV ✅ (שמור analysisId)
POST {{backendUrl}}/api/analysis/upload
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=VoiceBoundary

--VoiceBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="test_real.wav"
Content-Type: audio/wav

< ./test_files/test_real.wav
--VoiceBoundary--

###

### 3.2  Upload MP3 ✅
POST {{backendUrl}}/api/analysis/upload
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=VoiceBoundary

--VoiceBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="test_fake.mp3"
Content-Type: audio/mpeg

< ./test_files/test_fake.mp3
--VoiceBoundary--

###

### 3.3  Upload — Admin ✅
POST {{backendUrl}}/api/analysis/upload
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=VoiceBoundary

--VoiceBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="admin_test.wav"
Content-Type: audio/wav

< ./test_files/test_real.wav
--VoiceBoundary--


###
### ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
###  SECTION 4 │ ANALYSIS — NEGATIVE TESTS
### ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### 4.1  Upload ללא token ❌ (צפוי: 401)
POST {{backendUrl}}/api/analysis/upload
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=VoiceBoundary

--VoiceBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="test.wav"
Content-Type: audio/wav

< ./test_files/test_real.wav
--VoiceBoundary--

###

### 4.2  Upload PDF ❌ (צפוי: 400 — סוג קובץ לא חוקי)
POST {{backendUrl}}/api/analysis/upload
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=VoiceBoundary

--VoiceBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="not_audio.pdf"
Content-Type: application/pdf

< ./test_files/dummy.pdf
--VoiceBoundary--

###

### 4.3  Upload קובץ ריק ❌ (צפוי: 400)
POST {{backendUrl}}/api/analysis/upload
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=VoiceBoundary

--VoiceBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="empty.wav"
Content-Type: audio/wav

--VoiceBoundary--


###
### ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
###  SECTION 5 │ ANALYSIS HISTORY
### ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### 5.1  היסטוריה — User ✅
GET {{backendUrl}}/api/analysis/history
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

###

### 5.2  היסטוריה — Admin ✅
GET {{backendUrl}}/api/analysis/history
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### 5.3  היסטוריה ללא token ❌ (צפוי: 401)
GET {{backendUrl}}/api/analysis/history

###

### 5.4  ניתוח ספציפי ✅
GET {{backendUrl}}/api/analysis/{{analysisId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

###

### 5.5  IDOR — גישה לניתוח של משתמש אחר ❌ (צפוי: 404)
###       ⚠ שנה ל-ID של ניתוח של admin
GET {{backendUrl}}/api/analysis/1
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}
